The '''Basilisk''', also known as the '''SAURIA''', is an enemy in the original ''[[Final Fantasy]]''. They may first be encountered in the [[Cardian Islands]] and [[Citadel of Trials]] regions in the swamp. They later appear in [[Chaos Shrine (Final Fantasy)|Chaos Shrine]], on floor B1, as a rare [[random encounter|encounter]].

