== Strategy ==
[[File:Basilisk FF1.jpg|thumb|Concept artwork by [[Yoshitaka Amano]].]]
[[Attack (command)#Final Fantasy|Physical attacks]] are the primary way to defeat these enemies; magic can be saved for the more difficult encounters in the Chaos Shrine. Due to their average Defense, Basilisks are not hard to defeat. Basilisks use Gaze to [[Stone (Final Fantasy status)|petrify]] party members, but they also [[item drop|drop]] [[Gold Needle (Final Fantasy)|Gold Needle]]s upon defeat.

